<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>179</hymn_number>
<author>Upa Zasiama</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw Lal Isu, sietlei gamdai ah;
 Lungngaih tin cheng khuom bang do in
 Ei pui in aw, Na lampi-ah
 Aw ka Lal Isu.

[V2]
 Thihna luiah ei pui kaiin
 Lungngaih kahna khel gam nuomah
 Lungtuok sam gibang khente tawh
 Dawn bang kituok khawm di'n.

[V3]
 2. Simlei khulsin luonthi nulna hi,
 Sanggah liengthei kei ka kahna,
 Pak bang tuoi hen nuoi simlei hi.
 Lungngaih ka kahna.

[V4]
 3. Aw ka ngaih ka Lalpa anga chun,
 Chang bang kikhenna um lo-in;
 Henkawl nang bang ei sutpa chu,
 Zaila'n awi hitiu.

[V5]
 4. Zingdawng Sawl No, Hukdampa Lalpa,
 Ka lunggil gilo thim ahin;
 Hung vak inla, Na gam thiengtho,
 Chu ka muh theihnan.</lyrics>
<title>Sietlei Gamdai Ah!</title>
</song>